            "tab_con": "Establishment",
            "tab_con_font": "",
            "title": "Beyond Mobility. Beyond Limits.",
            "content": "Thunder Pro was born as the next evolution of Thunder, crafted for riders who demand more power, capability, and confidence. Driven by the same spirit of adventure and everyday practicality, it pushes the original vision further through refined engineering. From rugged trails and snowy paths to city streets, Thunder Pro delivers one seamless ride without compromise."
