            "tab_con": "Design",
            "tab_con_font": "",
            "title": "Designed for Power, Built for Control",
            "content": "Every design decision behind Thunder Pro balances high-output electric power with rider confidence. The eBike frame geometry is precisely engineered to support high-speed performance, heavy payloads, and long-distance riding, while maintaining stability and comfort. Dual suspension, 26″×4″ fat tires, and hydraulic disc brakes are integrated from the ground up—not added later—ensuring a fully optimized all-terrain electric bike system that performs as one unified machine."
          }
        },
        "item_XkRWcY": {
