            "tab_con": "Finished Product",
            "tab_con_font": "",
            "title": "Go Beyond Every Ride.",
            "content": "The result is Thunder Pro—a powerful, refined electric bike built to dominate streets and trails alike. With 1800W peak power, 35 MPH performance, dual suspension, hydraulic braking, and a 90-mile max range, it delivers an uncompromising ride that’s fast, capable, and comfortable. Designed to carry more, go farther, and ride harder—Thunder Pro is performance, perfected."
          }
        }
