          }
        },
        "text_wJh6U6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Equipped with a 1040Wh battery, Thunder Pro ST delivers a top speed of 35 mph and a maximum range of up to 90 miles, making it ideal for long commutes or all-day adventures. With fast charging from 15% to 80% in just 5 hours, you spend less time waiting and more time riding. Go farther, ride faster, and enjoy every journey without limits.</p>",
