        "text_mfcnAt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A responsive front suspension and upgraded rear soft-tail system absorb bumps and rough terrain for a smoother, more comfortable ride. Built to handle hard landings and tough trails, the rear suspension keeps the frame stable while reducing wear and maintenance. Paired with 26″×4″ fat tires, it delivers confident control and all-terrain comfort—so you can focus on the ride, not the road.</p>",
